The quality is fine, remember these were originally ripped from a VHS. As for episodes K01 - K03 are at this point to my knowledge, "lost". I'm sure Jim Mallon has them tucked away safely, but that does none of us any good. This is as close to the full collection as we can get. K00 was only recently aired in front of a live audience, which is how this bundle has it.

Bigevil, You are incorrect, there is NO Season 11. The show ended with "Merlin's Shop of Mystical Wonders", Season 10, Episode 13 on 9/12/1999

The episode you refer to, where Joel comes back shortly, is in Season 10.

Just to clarify there are 11 Seasons total, Starting with KTMA (local), then 1 through 10 (national).

For the record, utternerd is right about Merlin's Shop of Mystical Wonders -- it was the last episode aired -- but numerically it's #1003 -- it was passed over for some reason and actually aired after the "final episode."
